name: DVNO
wikiSummary: According to band member Xavier de Rosnay, "DVNO" stands for "Divino." de Rosnay states, "In every suburb of the world, in every city, there's always a nightclub called El Divino... Clubs where you have to wear a white shirt to get in." The vocalist featured in the song is Mehdi Pinson from the band Scenario Rock.
